comment: She has been exposed as a horrible person and an even worse actress.  He'd play that mermaid like nobody else ever could and it would engage an audience that would otherwise have had no interest in this sequel.  He needs to get his career back and the best start would be in seeing his face in the only role she performed that even comes to my mind. It would be huge. It would pay off. I would immensely enjoy it.
